                jQuery(".otro-bloque img").attr("srcset", datos.e).attr("src", datos.e).animate({opacity: "0"}).animate({opacity: "1"});
                jQuery(".qr-empresa img").attr("srcset", datos.o).attr("src", datos.o).animate({opacity: "0"}).animate({opacity: "1"});
                jQuery(".texto1").text(datos.texto1);
                jQuery(".texto2").text(datos.texto2);
                jQuery(".direccion").text(datos.direccion);
                jQuery(".telefono").text(datos.telefono);
                jQuery("#pagina-web").attr("href", datos.url);
            }
        
            // Variable para rastrear el país activo
            let paisActivo = null;
        
            // Función para resaltar el país seleccionado
            function resaltarPais(selector, textoSelector) {
                if (paisActivo) {
                    jQuery(paisActivo.selector).css({
                        "background-color": "transparent"
                    });
                    jQuery(paisActivo.textoSelector).css({
                        "color": "#333333" // Resetear color de texto
                    });
                }
                paisActivo = {selector, textoSelector}; // Actualizar país activo
                jQuery(selector).css({
                    "background-color": "#669933" // Fondo verde para el botón activo
                });
                jQuery(textoSelector).css({
                    "color": "#ffffff" // Cambiar color de texto
                });
            }
        
            // Configurar Colombia como país activo por defecto
            actualizarContenido(colombia);
            resaltarPais(colombia.selector, colombia.textoSelector);
        
            // Añadir eventos de clic para cada país
            jQuery(colombia.selector).click(function(){
                actualizarContenido(colombia);
                resaltarPais(colombia.selector, colombia.textoSelector);
            });
        
            jQuery(peru.selector).click(function(){
                actualizarContenido(peru);
                resaltarPais(peru.selector, peru.textoSelector);
            });
        
            jQuery(ecuador.selector).click(function(){
                actualizarContenido(ecuador);
                resaltarPais(ecuador.selector, ecuador.textoSelector);
            });
        
            jQuery(panama.selector).click(function(){
                actualizarContenido(panama);
                resaltarPais(panama.selector, panama.textoSelector);
            });
        
            jQuery(mexico.selector).click(function(){
                actualizarContenido(mexico);
                resaltarPais(mexico.selector, mexico.textoSelector);
            });
        
            jQuery(usa.selector).click(function(){
                actualizarContenido(usa);
                resaltarPais(usa.selector, usa.textoSelector);
            });
        });</script> </div></div></div><div class="has_eae_slider elementor-element elementor-element-147478cc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="147478cc" data-element_type="container"><div class="has_eae_slider elementor-element elementor-element-65e114ba e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="65e114ba" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5845ff81 qr-empresa exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="5845ff81" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container">

                 const [directLineURL, token] = await Promise.all([
                   fetch(new URL(`/powervirtualagents/regionalchannelsettings?api-version=${apiVersion}`, tokenEndpointURL))
                     .then(response => {
                       if (!response.ok) {
                         throw new Error('Failed to retrieve regional channel settings.');
                       }
        
                       return response.json();
                     })
                     .then(({ channelUrlsById: { directline } }) => directline),
                   fetch(tokenEndpointURL)
                     .then(response => {
                       if (!response.ok) {
                         throw new Error('Failed to retrieve Direct Line token.');
                       }
        
                       return response.json();
                     })
                     .then(({ token }) => token)
                 ]);
        
                
        
                 const directLine = WebChat.createDirectLine({ domain: new URL('v3/directline', directLineURL), token });
        
                
        
                 const subscription = directLine.connectionStatus$.subscribe({
                   next(value) {
                     if (value === 2) {
                       directLine
                         .postActivity({
                           localTimezone: Intl.DateTimeFormat().resolvedOptions().timeZone,
                           locale,
                           name: 'startConversation',
                           type: 'event'
                         })
                         .subscribe();
        
                       // Only send the event once, unsubscribe after the event is sent.
                       subscription.unsubscribe();
                     }
                   }
                 });
        
                 WebChat.renderWebChat({ directLine, locale, styleOptions }, document.getElementById('webchat'));
               })();
               
                document.getElementById('chatIcon').addEventListener('click', () => {
                    document.getElementById('popupBackground').style.display = 'flex';
                });
        
                document.getElementById('closePopup').addEventListener('click', () => {
                    document.getElementById('popupBackground').style.display = 'none';
                });</script> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="has_eae_slider elementor-element elementor-element-6058953 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="6058953" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-48e53ae exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-template" data-id="48e53ae" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="template.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-template"><div data-elementor-type="section" data-elementor-id="4850" class="elementor elementor-4850" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library"><div class="has_eae_slider elementor-element elementor-element-cbfa12f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent" data-id="cbfa12f" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;position&quot;:&quot;fixed&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-073b69e exad-sticky-section-no exad-glass-effect-no elementor-widget elementor-widget-html" data-id="073b69e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="html.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"> <script>jQuery(document).ready(function($) {
